    "created_at": "2016-06-07T00:49:51Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-06-07T00:49:51Z",
    "body": "Chromium renders the page by first drawing the background color and then the actual page, and the rendering only starts when the page shows for the first time. So no matter how long you wait you will still see the white flash, the only solution is to set a background color for your app, which can effectively remove the flash.\n"
